author: Alemas
title: First to review again!
review:
This set is pretty cool, with adjustable winglets, trans-blue 1x1 round plates, cool sides, and a pull-back motor!

Pros:

Cool design
Adjustable winglets
Cool sides
Cool wheels

Cons:

None!

Overall, a great set!

author: Zapp_Brannigan
title: Nice
review: This race car was pretty cool. It comes with pre-printed elements, special blue lights, medium Technic wheels with small gears for hubcaps, adjustable fins and a wind back motor. The overall design is very sleek. You can combine it with 8382 to make an 8 wheel race car.
